<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA83">
<l>iṉiyavaṉ māya ṉeṉavuraippa rēlu</l>
<l>miṉiyavaṉ kāṇpariya ṉēlu – miṉiyavaṉ</l>
<l>kaḷḷattāṉ maṇkoṇṭu viṇkaṭanta paiṅkaḻalā</l>
<l>ṉuḷḷatti ṉuḷḷē yuḷaṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though now they say that he is the Dark one,</l>
<l>even though now he is difficult to see, he now [already]</l>
<l>is inside [my] heart, he with the green-golden anklets</l>
<l>who by [his] guile took the earth [and] crossed the sky.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
